01:23:01,727 --> 01:23:05,188
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}How they had to be beaten out of every country they ever occupied.

1258
01:23:05,272 --> 01:23:08,483
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}How this prison was just an extension of their system.

1259
01:23:08,567 --> 01:23:11,152
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Calling for work on the threes.

1260
01:23:11,570 --> 01:23:14,656
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We had to confront the chief prison officer, Barker.

1261
01:23:14,740 --> 01:23:15,823
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Mr. Smalls.

1262
01:23:15,908 --> 01:23:18,743
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But to do that, we had to take care of Ronnie Smalls.

1263
01:23:19,036 --> 01:23:21,704
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Can I have a word about 54, Halsley Road?

1264
01:23:25,459 --> 01:23:26,876
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Take a walk.

1265
01:23:35,094 --> 01:23:37,970
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}If anything happens to me or Gerry

1266
01:23:39,348 --> 01:23:41,474
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}or any other Irish prisoner,

1267
01:23:42,309 --> 01:23:46,020
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}we'll have 54, Halsley Road blown to smithereens

