01:23:50,609 --> 01:23:53,277
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Threaten my family and I'll cut your fucking head off.

1270
01:23:56,990 --> 01:23:58,574
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I don't make threats.

1271
01:23:58,659 --> 01:24:00,618
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I just carry out orders.

1272
01:24:01,120 --> 01:24:02,662
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I don't want to hurt your family.

1273
01:24:07,918 --> 01:24:11,504
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Your trouble is, Joe, you want to rule the fucking world.

1274
01:24:13,424 --> 01:24:14,549
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Paddy's all right.

1275
01:24:26,395 --> 01:24:29,188
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Soon, we were all one happy family.

1276
01:24:29,314 --> 01:24:30,356
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Again!

1277
01:24:30,441 --> 01:24:32,775
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Even Kojak was ready to forgive.

1278
01:24:33,026 --> 01:24:34,360
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Live and let live.

1279
01:24:34,486 --> 01:24:35,737
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Barker began to panic.

1280
01:24:36,530 --> 01:24:38,614
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}He told us to take our socks out of the window.

1281
01:24:38,699 --> 01:24:41,242
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}He thought we were signaling to other prisoners.

1282
01:24:41,535 --> 01:24:44,287
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}We're not signaling. We're drying our socks out.

1283
01:24:44,371 --> 01:24:46,122
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Take the socks out of the window. Who says?

1284
01:24:46,457 --> 01:24:47,623
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Mr. Barker.

1285
01:24:47,708 --> 01:24:50,001
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}That was all the excuse Joe needed.

1286
01:24:50,085 --> 01:24:51,335
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Give us two minutes.

1287
01:24:51,879 --> 01:24:53,963
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Hey, up and away we went. Are you with me?

1288
01:24:54,256 --> 01:24:55,381
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}What's he up to now?

1289
01:24:59,261 --> 01:25:01,596
{\fncambria\fs22\shad2\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}All prison officers to vacate the wing.

